# Movies App

Android app to browse and view details of trending and upcoming movies using the TMDb API.

## Features

- Fetch and display latest movies
- View details: title, release date, overview, rating
- Uses modern Android development stack

## Screenshots
##Not available

## Tech Stack

- **Language**: Kotlin
- **UI**: Jetpack Compose
- **Architecture**: MVVM
- **Dependency Injection**: Hilt
- **Networking**: Retrofit + Gson
- **Image Loading**: Coil
- **Navigation**: Jetpack Navigation

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Android Studio Hedgehog or newer
- Minimum SDK 24
- TMDb API key

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/ogunjembola/Movies.git
